{
  "message": "chore(beads): rotate stale br_history snapshots (2026-03-15)\n\nRotates out 22 br history snapshots from 2026-03-15 (eleven\n`issues.20260315_*.jsonl` files and their matching `.meta.json`\nsiblings). The `.beads/.br_history/` directory is br's dated\nbackup store for the canonical `.beads/issues.jsonl`; older\nsnapshots get pruned periodically so the history directory does\nnot grow without bound.\n\nNo issue data is lost: the current `.beads/issues.jsonl` remains\nthe source of truth (and newer snapshots from 2026-03-16 onward\nare kept in `.br_history/`). This matches the pattern established\nby prior commits such as `chore(beads): sync issues.jsonl + rotate\nstale br_history snapshots` (30af976) and `chore(beads): mark\nbd-bxba in_progress, rotate br_history snapshot` (1f4da3e).",
